model

Class Door

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Piece
      • model.Door

  • public class Door
extends Piece
    This class represents the Doors in the game. Door is used to traverse from one room to another. Door objects maintain a collection of keys that can unlock it, the door can only be unlocked by a player if they possess a valid key.
    Author:
    Harman (singhharm1)
